00:27:20.650 --> 00:27:22.540
OK, but wait a minute.

00:27:22.540 --> 00:27:27.940
Organizations are much more
complex than are individuals.

00:27:27.940 --> 00:27:30.190
That is, you can get a bunch
of happy people together.

00:27:30.190 --> 00:27:33.140
It does not make for
a great organization.

00:27:33.140 --> 00:27:35.050
So the question is,
does this actually

00:27:35.050 --> 00:27:37.990
work in organizations,
when I'm held

00:27:37.990 --> 00:27:41.350
accountable for profitability,
and productivity, and quality,

00:27:41.350 --> 00:27:43.960
and customer
satisfaction, and so on?

00:27:43.960 --> 00:27:46.210
That's been my
research for 15 years.

00:27:46.210 --> 00:27:47.770
That's been the question.

00:27:47.770 --> 00:27:49.720
Yeah, but does it
work in organizations?

00:27:49.720 --> 00:27:54.370
Turns out, after 15
years, the bottom line

00:27:54.370 --> 00:27:58.330
is if you implement
in an organization

00:27:58.330 --> 00:27:59.980
positive practices--

00:27:59.980 --> 00:28:02.740
we haven't talked about
what that is at all.

00:28:02.740 --> 00:28:09.200
But virtuous practices,
compassion, kindness,

00:28:09.200 --> 00:28:13.150
forgiveness,
gratitude, and so on.

00:28:13.150 --> 00:28:16.450
You will get higher
levels of profitability.

00:28:16.450 --> 00:28:19.990
You make more money by far
than the industry average.

00:28:19.990 --> 00:28:23.020
Productivity is
significantly improved.

00:28:23.020 --> 00:28:28.190
Quality goes up, fewer errors,
less waste, fewer mistakes.

00:28:28.190 --> 00:28:33.460
Innovation, new product ideas,
creativity, all improve.

00:28:33.460 --> 00:28:35.590
The scores on creativity go up.

00:28:35.590 --> 00:28:39.640
Customer satisfaction, customer
loyalty, customer retention

00:28:39.640 --> 00:28:40.690
goes up.

00:28:40.690 --> 00:28:44.870
Employee satisfaction,
employee retention all go up.

00:28:44.870 --> 00:28:47.350
That is-- that's what
you're held accountable for.

00:28:47.350 --> 00:28:49.570
All of those are
significantly improved

00:28:49.570 --> 00:28:51.970
when you implement
positive practices.

00:28:51.970 --> 00:28:55.900
I'm going to not show you
hardly any of the research.

