00:30:08.259 --> 00:30:08.800
But we could.

00:30:08.800 --> 00:30:10.890
Plus a bunch of other
things, turn over,

00:30:10.890 --> 00:30:13.920
and you know, satisfaction,
and all those kinds of things.

00:30:13.920 --> 00:30:18.570
That is, even in the least
likely and most hostile

00:30:18.570 --> 00:30:22.210
