00:30:24.410 --> 00:30:25.950
But over a two-year
period of time,

00:30:25.950 --> 00:30:28.605
double digit improvement,
where the industry average

00:30:28.605 --> 00:30:31.290
is 1% or 2%, double
digit improvement

00:30:31.290 --> 00:30:33.960
on these various dimensions
that really count,

00:30:33.960 --> 00:30:36.760
that people want to improve.

00:30:36.760 --> 00:30:40.560
So the whole point is, with
only a very small sampling

00:30:40.560 --> 00:30:44.730
