we know is actually,

00:30:44.730 --> 00:30:48.730
positive practices pay off
physically, cognitively,

00:30:48.730 --> 00:30:52.800
socially, and they pay
off organizationally.

00:30:52.800 --> 00:30:54.390
When you implement
positive practices,

00:30:54.390 --> 00:30:57.000
organizations do better.

00:30:57.000 --> 00:30:58.916
We improve what we want--

00:30:58.916 --> 00:31:01.290
what we're held accountable
for, what we want to improve.

